  <p><img src="doc-files/GridLayout-2.gif" alt="Shows 6 buttons in rows of 2. Row 1 shows buttons 2 then 1.
        Row 2 shows buttons 4 then 3. Row 3 shows buttons 6 then 5."> </p>
  <p>Figure 2: Horizontal, Right-to-Left </p>
 </div> 
